text: Maria Teresa Aquino-Oreta (born Maria Teresa Aquino Aquino) (June 28, 1944 - May 14, 2020), better known as Tessie Aquino-Oreta, was a Filipino Liberal politician. She was born in Concepcion, Tarlac. She was a member of the House of Representatives of the Philippines from 1987 to 1998 and Senator from 1988 to 2004. Aquino-Oreta died on May 14, 2020 in Manila at the age of 75.Former Sen. Tessie Oreta passes away ==References== Category:1944 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Central Luzon
